  "texts": [
    "In front of this strong awareness about the importance of exploring the new opportunities of LLMs in the business process communities, the implementation of the LLM-based approach in processbased DSSs is still missed.",
    "According to this, the present study represents a novelty with respect to the more recent literature since it introduces and experiments with an LLM model to improve the efficiency of DSS.",
    "The study also proposes, for the first time in the business process representation, the adoption of RAG integrated in the LLM model to ensure a greater adherence with the specific aspects of the business process domain.",
    "Finally, the impact of the proposed approach within its components is evaluated and discussed.",
    "Background Business Process models and descriptionA process model serves as a representation of the business process structure, encompassing the activities to be executed and the constraints governing their sequence."
